It’s not because of the lack of ingredients.  It’s because we have too many ingredients. Too much egg white.

109
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,600

110
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,440
# 我们给它上浆
Tenderize the meat with starch and egg white

111
