How to know that the meat is well-tenderized. Tip 1 is that you can feel the drag when you sir it

116
00:05:57,320 --> 00:06:02,720
# 黏糊了 也说明这淀粉全覆在肉上了
Number two, it looks sticky which means the meat is all covered by starch

117
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,120
# 水滑的时候
When we cook meat in water

118
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:06,720
# 这淀粉略微的要比炒菜的淀粉
We need a little bit more starch than we use for stir fries

119
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,360
# 略微的多一点
A little bit more

120
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:11,040
