# 这个不用拿油封 炒菜可以拿油封上
Don’t need to add oil in. If you want to make stir fries you can add some oil.

123
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:19,800
# （用油封）下锅容易散（不易粘连）
Meat can fall apart easily (not stick together) in the pot with oil

124
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,960
# 这个就不用了是吧
We don’t use oil this time

125
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:26,000
