I forgot! Add white pepper powder

126
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:29,760
# 这银耳我们有的人爱吃冰糖银耳
Some people like eating white wood mushroom with white rock sugar

127
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,960
