Don’t put sugar too early

128
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:35,040
# 白糖冰糖都不能早放 后放
No matter what sugar it is

129
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:38,240
# 先把银耳蒸烂 然后再放冰糖再蒸
Get the white wood mushroom cooked first. Then add sugar and steam again.

130
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:41,840
# 那银耳蒸出来以后软糯滑
This way the white wood mushroom will be super smooth

131
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:45,600
# 我们在涨发干货的时候 不要用热水
Do not use hot water to re-hydrate dried food

132
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:49,480
