Don’t rush. You can start earlier with cold water

133
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:52,880
# 提前两三个小时给它泡上
Re-hydrate it two or three hours in advance

134
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,280
# 这干货的东西
For dried food

135
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:56,840
# 一定要用凉水让它慢慢回软
You have to use cold water to re-hydrate it slowly

136
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:59,120
