We also got a small size steam pot. This pot is pretty interesting

151
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:37,440
# 以前就是紫砂 现在改成白砂
It used to be made of purple sand and nowadays it’s made of white sand

152
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:40,360
# 这也挺精致的 这是每人一位的
Looks delicate. One per person.

153
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:43,040
# 开锅烫银耳
Cook white wood mushroom with boiled water

154
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:45,200
# 其实在家里头如果没有汽锅
If you don’t have steam pot at home

155
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:48,720
