Put ingredients all inside the pot and steam

158
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:57,680
# 不用等它开 烫一下就行 有个三五分钟
Don’t need to wait water to boil again. 3 to 5 five minutes are enough

159
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,280
# 也不用去冲凉
Don’t need use cold water to cool down

160
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:01,240
# 下面就着这水
Now we will still use the water

161
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,840
# 这个肉下锅的时候别动它
Don’t stir meat once you put meat in the pot

162
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:08,320
# 用水慢慢把它拖熟 散开放
Use water to cook it. Put it in separately

163
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:11,040
# 它在不断的有变化
It’s changing continuously

164
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:13,000

165
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,240
# 它是一球一球的
They are separate chicken cubes

166
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:19,360
# 一动不要紧那淀粉就下来
Don’t touch it or the starch will get off

167
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:24,040
# 就是因为你给它 排刀
Because you scored the meat

168
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:28,960
# 排刀以后它经过一紧 就变成球了
Once it’s heated, the meat will contract and roll into ball.

169
